iming to accelerate development and minimize technical lapses.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/prayagraj-development-authority-to-establish-project-management-unit-for-streamlined-urban-planning/129889812?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-16090/129889812.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}